show.title: CEO, Those Twins Look Like You

show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: A young CEO takes in a troubled girl, only to discover her identical twin on the streets. Both bear the haunting face of his late fiancée. As he searches for answers, buried secrets resurface revealing a deadly past, a web of lies, and the chilling truth: her death was no accident… and the twins may be the key to everything.
